    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>You're not supplying it with an array in your example. The following compiles fine:</p>\n\n<pre><code>public @interface SampleAnnotation {\n    String[] sampleValues();\n}\n\npublic class Values {\n    public static final String val0 = \"A\";\n    public static final String val1 = \"B\";\n\n    @SampleAnnotation(sampleValues={ val0, val1 })\n    public void foo() {\n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
